src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Midday' game
03 Nov 2019, 18:04 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday afternoon's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 3 Midday" game were:
1-1-5
(one, one, five)
